snippet: Adrienne Motley and Erykah Davenport scored 15 points apiece, and No. 11 Miami outscored Coppin State 16-2 in the fourth quarter for a 75-35 victory on Monday night in the Miami Holiday Tournament....
lead_paragraph: Adrienne Motley and Erykah Davenport scored 15 points apiece, and No. 11 Miami outscored Coppin State 16-2 in the fourth quarter for a 75-35 victory on Monday night in the Miami Holiday Tournament.

headline.main: No. 11 Miami Women Keep Coppin State Winless, 75-35
